name: Martial Arts Returnees Game Broadcast
summary: [TS] Martial Arts Returnees Game Broadcast follows a martial artist who, after returning to modern society and undergoing a gender transformation, becomes a game streamer. The story mixes martial arts with gaming and live-streaming elements in a contemporary fantasy setting.
